PrecisRegulations Amending the BOATING RESTRICTION REGULATIONS by establishing a shoreline speed limit of 10 km/h on all inland waters in British Columbia, applying that same limit to the waters of False Creek in Vancouver, and placing False Creek on the schedule of waters for which a permit is required to hold a regatta, marine parade or boat race.
